      "text": "The goal is to show the simplicity of iconic arithmetic with an abundance of examples in order to convey a single message: **the entire content of school mathematics can be described by a few definitions that anchor how iconic constants might behave, supported by three visually simple pattern-recognition axioms that animate the behavior and transformation of [[James forms]]**.\n\n"
